headline: Jacobs Selected to Strengthen Transmission and Distribution Infrastructure for Bonneville Power Administration
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected by Bonneville Power Administration (BPA) to provide engineering and advisory services for the Grand Coulee Modernization Program, a critical initiative aimed at enhancing the reliability, efficiency, and longevity of transmission and distribution infrastructure supporting the largest power-generating dam in the U.S.
